title: (OCE) LF Jungle for ranked flex + tournaments
body:
Hey guys, we've got a solid group of 4 atm and are looking for a competent Jungler to fill the last spot.

Looking to grind some flex and join tournaments.

Requirements:
- Must have discord with mic
- 18+
- Gold 5+ (Can be lenient if slightly lower)

Add me on league please.

Cheers!

League Name: CrimFaker
